snippet.textDisplay: hope you all get well soon Mike ,keep following your videos.It is really unreasonable and something can not be understood like there is no place for quarantine but you were taken out to wait. speechless...by the way,小麦is soooooooo cute,love his voice,hope this can make you feel better,there is nothing like staying with the people you love.hope all these things pass quickly1!!hope we could live a normal life.
